description: View key ECS ContainerInsights metrics with an out of the box dashboard.
title: ECS ContainerInsights

51f4fa2b-89c7-47c2-9795-f32cffaab985.name: Account
51f4fa2b-89c7-47c2-9795-f32cffaab985.queryValue:
SELECT DISTINCT JSONExtractString(labels, 'cloud_account_id') AS cloud_account_id
FROM signoz_metrics.distributed_time_series_v4_1day
WHERE metric_name = 'aws_ECS_MemoryUtilization_max' GROUP BY cloud_account_id

9faf0f4b-b245-4b3c-83a3-60cfa76dfeb0.name: Region
9faf0f4b-b245-4b3c-83a3-60cfa76dfeb0.queryValue:
SELECT DISTINCT JSONExtractString(labels, 'cloud_region') AS region
FROM signoz_metrics.distributed_time_series_v4_1day
WHERE metric_name = 'aws_ECS_MemoryUtilization_max' AND JSONExtractString(labels, 'cloud_account_id') IN {{.Account}} GROUP BY region

bfbdbcbe-a168-4d81-b108-36339e249116.name: Cluster
bfbdbcbe-a168-4d81-b108-36339e249116.queryValue:
SELECT DISTINCT JSONExtractString(labels, 'ClusterName') AS cluster
FROM signoz_metrics.distributed_time_series_v4_1day
WHERE metric_name like '%aws_ECS%' AND JSONExtractString(labels, 'cloud_account_id') IN {{.Account}} AND JSONExtractString(labels, 'cloud_region') IN {{.Region}}
GROUP BY cluster
